0.06 2018-10-02
 - Port from Moose to Moo + Types::Standard, as no Moose-specific 
   features are needed. Should be backwards compatible (pplu + waterkip)

0.05 2018-10-02
 - token command-line option can now be dynamically generated 
   on each invocation passing a CodeRef (ureesoriano)

0.04 2018-10-01
 - token attribute was being ignored (ureesoriano)

0.03 2018-09-25
 - Ability to set a kubeconfig via an attribute (waterkip)
   The namespace parameter no longer gets a default value (if
   you don't specify it, it will get it's default value from
   kubectl, which is normally 'default', but can be overwritten
   in the kubeconfig file)

0.02 2018-05-15
 - Add Test::Exception to test dependencies

0.01 2018-05-10
 - First release into an unsuspecting world
